----------------------------------------------------------------
doc:
----------------------------------------------------------------
This directory includes three files with documentation:
- The examplation of the theory.
- A introduction to the tool, the usage of the applications and some commented examples.
- An abstraction pattern for the parallel composition of similar processes.

----------------------------------------------------------------
examples: 
----------------------------------------------------------------
This directory includes three different applications with the scripts to run them. Information about the examples can be found in the documentation.

---------------------------------------------------------------- 
src:
----------------------------------------------------------------
This directory includes the source files.

